					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is great, especially the MTF's mascot. +1.</p> <p>One minor point - the &quot;Note: No such trademark exists&quot; doesn't make sense, since anyone can create an unregistered trademark. You'd need to change (TM) to ® for it to be searchable for the Foundation to determine its existence or lack thereof.</p> 
